      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA CELESTE (7) is a handy type who notched her 8th career success when too good (27.71) from Box 5 at this track. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Shapes as a top winning chance on latest effort. WARREGO STORM (1) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 27.85 beating Weblec Max. Has a strong record out of this box with four wins and two minor placings from seven starts. One of the prime contenders. GOUDA MONELLI (2) had to overcome a collision with another runner and could manage only a distant fifth (28.01) in a Grade 5 over 488m at this track. Can measure up this time. RAPIDO KUNA (8) will give backers a sight.",
